What you need to know:

Athletics Kenya (AK) Central Rift secretary general Kennedy Tanui disclosed that close to 200 junior athletes drawn from three camps and schools are expected at the one-day eventAmong the juniors for the event is the reigning East Africa Secondary Schools 800m and 400m champion Nelly JepchirchirThe national trials for the world junior event will be held July 1 to 2 at the Nyayo National Stadium